1. Build the application:
	a. Go to the project folder
	b. Issue the command 'mvn clean package'
2. Run the application:
	a. Go to the project/target folder
	b. Issue the command java -jar numberencoding-1.0.jar path_to_the_input_file path_to_the_dictionary_file
		Example: java -jar numberencoding-1.0.jar input.txt dictionary.txt

============================================================================================================
Used technologies:
	Java 8,
	JUnit 4.12